  <script type="text/javascript">
   function loadIframe(iframeName, url) {
                var $iframe = $('#' + iframeName);
                if ( $iframe.length ) {
                    $iframe.attr('src',url);   
                    return false;
                }
                return true;
            }
    
            // Show/Hide SignIn overlay panel.
            $(document).ready(function(){
                var clickedSignin = false;
                $("#rewardsDropDown").click(function(e){
                    if ($(".signinsignuplabel").is(":visible")) {
                        $("#currencylist").hide();
                        $("#Lang2794Div").hide();
                        clickedSignin = true;
                        if($(".signinOnTop").hasClass("hide")){
                            $('.signinOnTop').removeClass("hide");
                            var iframeUrl = $("div.signinOnTop").data().url;
                            var iframeUrlSrc = $("#frmsignin").attr("src");
                            if(!iframeUrlSrc &amp;&amp; iframeUrlSrc.length == 0){
                                e.stopPropagation();
                                $("#frmsignin").attr("src", iframeUrl);
                                loadIframe('frmsignin','https://www.agoda.com/rewards/signinv2.html')
                            }
                        }
                        else {
                            $('.signinOnTop').addClass("hide"); 
                        }                    
                    }
                });
                
                $('body').click(function(){
                    if(!clickedSignin) {
                        $('.signinOnTop').addClass("hide"); 
                    }
                    clickedSignin = false;
                });
            });
  </script>

             <script type="text/javascript">
              $(document).ready(function () {
            // Get a reference to the container.
            var container = $("#Lang2794Div");

            $("#langselect").click(function (e) {
                if (container.is(":visible")) {
                    // Hide - slide up.
                    container.hide();
                    $(this).removeClass("langselect_active");
                    e.stopPropagation();
                } else {
                    // Show - slide down.
                    container.show();
                    $(this).addClass("langselect_active");

                    $("html").click(function () {
                        if (container.hasClass("block")) {
                            container.show();
                        }
                        else {
                            container.hide();
                            $("#langselect").removeClass("langselect_active");
                        }
                    });

                    if (document.documentElement.addEventListener) {
                        var imgarrival = document.getElementById('imgarrival');
                        if (imgarrival != null) {
                            imgarrival.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                                if (container.is(":visible")) {
                                    // Hide - slide up.
                                    container.hide();
                                    $("#langselect").removeClass("langselect_active");
                                }
                            }, true);
                        }

                        var imgdepart = document.getElementById('imgdepart');
                        if (imgdepart != null) {
                            imgdepart.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                                if (container.is(":visible")) {
                                    // Hide - slide up.
                                    container.hide();
                                    $("#langselect").removeClass("langselect_active");
                                }
                            }, true);
                        }

                    } else {
                        document.documentElement.attachEvent('onpropertychange', function (e) {
                            var x = document.getElementById("ui-datepicker-div");
                            if (x != null &amp;&amp; x != "undefined") {
                                if (x.style.display == 'block') {
                                    if (container.is(":visible")) {
                                        // Hide - slide up.
                                        container.hide();
                                        $("#langselect").removeClass("langselect_active");
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }, false);


                        if ($.browser.version.substr(0, 1) == 8) {
                            if (document.getElementById("imgdepart") != null &amp;&amp; document.getElementById("imgdepart") != "undefined") {
                                document.getElementById("imgdepart").attachEvent('onmouseout', function (e) {
                                    if ($("#ui-datepicker-div").css("display") == 'block') {
                                        if (container.is(":visible")) {
                                            // Hide - slide up.
                                            container.hide();
                                            $("#langselect").removeClass("langselect_active");
                                        }
                                    }
                                });
                            }

                            if (document.getElementById("imgarrival") != null &amp;&amp; document.getElementById("imgarrival") != "undefined") {
                                document.getElementById("imgarrival").attachEvent('onmouseout', function (e) {
                                    if ($("#ui-datepicker-div").css("display") == 'block') {
                                        if (container.is(":visible")) {
                                            // Hide - slide up.
                                            container.hide();
                                            $("#langselect").removeClass("langselect_active");
                                        }
                                    }
                                });
                            }
                        }

                    }
                }
            });


            $("#langselect").mouseover(function () {
                container.addClass("block");
            }).mouseout(function () {
                container.removeClass("block");
            });

        });

             <script type="text/javascript">
              $(document).ready(function () {
        // Get a reference to the container.
        var container = $("#currencylist");

        $("#currencyselect").click(function (e) {

            
            if (container.is(":visible")) {
                // Hide - slide up.
                container.hide();
                $(this).removeClass("langselect_active");
                e.stopPropagation();
            } else {
                // Show - slide down.
                container.show();
                $(this).addClass("langselect_active");

                $("html").click(function () {
                    if (container.hasClass("block")) {
                        container.show();
                    }
                    else {
                        container.hide();
                        $("#currencyselect").removeClass("langselect_active");
                    }
                });
            }
            
        });


        $("#currencyselect").mouseover(function () {
            container.addClass("block");
        }).mouseout(function () {
            container.removeClass("block");
        });
    });

    function selectCurrency(currencyCode) {
        //Assign new selected currency code            
        $('#CurrDropdown').text(currencyCode);

        //showCurrency(false);
        //do post back to  a page.
        var btnCurrencyChange = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl00_ddlCurrency_btnCurrencyChange");
        var hidCurrencyChange = document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl00_ddlCurrency_hidCurrencyChange");

        hidCurrencyChange.value = currencyCode;
        btnCurrencyChange.click();
    }
             </script>

        }

        function displayMainPhoto(obj) {
            //hilighted red border
            $(".tagBorder").removeClass('hilighted');
            $(obj).parent().addClass('hilighted');

            //set index of HD image to be the same as thumnail index
            imgIndex = $(obj).attr('itemIndex');

            //Display Image
            imageFade();

            isHover = false;
        }

        function displayImage(controlID, photoURL) {
            var img = new Image();
                                   
            img.onload = function () {

                if (photoURL.indexOf("_800x600") &gt; -1 || photoURL.indexOf("840x460") &gt; -1) { //HD Image Agoda and B.com
                    $("#" + controlID).removeClass('STDimage').addClass('HDimage').attr("src", photoURL);
                }
                else if (photoURL.indexOf("max500") &gt; -1) { //STD for B.com
                    var top = (395 - img.height) / 2;
                    var left = (715 - img.width) / 2;

                    $("#" + controlID).attr("style", "top:" + top + "px; left:" + left + "px");
                    $("#" + controlID).removeClass('STDimage').removeClass('HDimage').attr("src", photoURL);
                }
                else { //STD for Agoda
                    if (photoURL.indexOf("s=800x600") &gt; -1) {
                        $("#" + controlID).removeClass('STDimage').addClass('HDimage').attr("src", photoURL);
                    } else{
                        $("#" + controlID).removeClass('HDimage').addClass('STDimage').attr("src", photoURL);
                    
                    } 

                    
                }
            }
            img.src = photoURL;

        }

        function hilightThumnail(imgIndex) {
            $(".tagBorder").removeClass('hilighted');
            $("img[itemIndex='" + imgIndex + "']").parent().addClass('hilighted');
        }

        function jumpToRangeImageIsSelected(imgIndex) {
            var rangeImage = Math.ceil(imgIndex / 9.0) - 1; //get range of image is displayed
            if (rangeImage &lt;= 0) {
                document.getElementById("thumbs").style.left = "0px";
            }
            else {
                document.getElementById("thumbs").style.left = Math.ceil(rangeImage * -630) + "px";
            }
        }

        function imageFade() {
            displayImage("hotelFade", photo[imgIndex]);
            $("#hotelFade").css("display", "");

            $("#hotelPic").stop(true, false).fadeOut(1000, function () {
                displayImage("hotelPic", photo[imgIndex]);
                $("#hotelPic").css("display", "");
                $("#hotelFade").css("display", "none");
            });
        }

        $(document).ready(function () {
            //display Image
            displayImage("hotelPic", photo[imgIndex]);

            if ('True' == 'True') {
                displayImage("hotelFade", photo[imgIndex]);
            }

            hilightThumnail(imgIndex);

            //default for first page loaded
            $(".pager_md_photo").removeAttr("style");

            //Event
            $("#hotelPic,.pager_md_photo, .hotel_photos_wrapper .unselect").mouseover(function () {
                $(".pager_md_photo").removeAttr("style");
                $('.review_container').stop(true, false).fadeOut(400);
                $('.reviews_panel').stop(true, false).fadeOut(400);
                isHover = true;
            });

            $("#hotelPic,.pager_md_photo, .hotel_photos_wrapper .unselect").mouseleave(function () {
                $(".pager_md_photo").attr("style", "display:none");
                $('.review_container').stop(true, false).fadeTo(500, 1);
                $('.reviews_panel').stop(true, false).fadeTo(500, 1);
                isHover = false;
            });

            $(".photo_md").mouseover(function () {
                isHover = true;
            });

            $(".photo_md").mouseleave(function () {
                isHover = false;
            });

            //Click next-photo in main 
            $("#next-photo").click(function () {
                imgIndex++;

                //index circling
                var isLastImage = false;
                if (imgIndex &gt; photo.length - 1) {
                    imgIndex = 0;
                    isLastImage = true;
                }

                //display Image
                imageFade();

                //CSS hilight thumnail
                hilightThumnail(imgIndex);

                //thumnail next page
                if (isLastImage) {
                    $("#next-thumbPhoto").click();
                }
                else if (imgIndex &gt; 8 &amp;&amp; photo.length &gt; 10 &amp;&amp; ((parseInt(imgIndex) - 10) / 9) % 1 == 0) { //from arithmetic sequences An = A1 + (n-1)d
                    $("#next-thumbPhoto").click();
                }

                //auto jump to range of image is selected
                jumpToRangeImageIsSelected(imgIndex);
            });

            //Click next-photo in main 
            $("#prev-photo").click(function () {
                imgIndex--;

                //index circling
                var isFirstImage = false;
                if (imgIndex &lt; 0) {
                    imgIndex = photo.length - 1;
                    isFirstImage = true;
                }

                //display Image
                imageFade();

                //CSS hilight thumnail
                hilightThumnail(imgIndex);

                //thumnail prev page
                if (isFirstImage) {
                    $("#prev-thumbPhoto").click();
                }
                else if (imgIndex &gt; 7 &amp;&amp; ((parseInt(imgIndex) + 1) / 9) % 1 == 0) { //from arithmetic sequences An = A1 + (n-1)d
                    $("#prev-thumbPhoto").click();
                }

                //auto jump to range of image is selected
                jumpToRangeImageIsSelected(imgIndex);
            });

            //keydown left/right to click prev/next photo
            $("body").keydown(function (e) {
                if (e.keyCode == 37) { // left
                    $("#prev-photo").click();
                }
                else if (e.keyCode == 39) { // right
                    $("#next-photo").click();
                }
            });
        });

        //var fadePhoto = setInterval(function () { fadeTimer() }, 7000);
      </script>

       <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function () {
        var isHover = false;
        var xPosiotion = 0;
        var allPicCount = $("span[id*='spPicCount']").text();
        var maxPicPositon = (parseInt(allPicCount) - 10) * -70;
        var lastThumbPhotoPage = Math.ceil((parseInt(allPicCount) - 11) / 9);

        if ($("span[id*='spPicCount']").text() != "" &amp;&amp; $("span[id*='spPicCount']").text() &gt; 10) {

            $(".hotel_thumbnails_AB2659,.thumb_container").mouseover(function () {
            $(".pager_md_thumbPhoto").removeAttr("style");
            isHover = true;
        });

            $(".hotel_thumbnails_AB2659,.thumb_container").mouseleave(function () {
            $(".pager_md_thumbPhoto").attr("style", "display:none");
            isHover = false;
        });

        $("#next-thumbPhoto").click(function () {
            if (xPosiotion &gt; maxPicPositon) {
                    xPosiotion -= 70 * 9;
                } else {
                    xPosiotion = 0;
            }
                document.getElementById("thumbs").style.left = parseInt(xPosiotion) + "px";
        });

        $("#prev-thumbPhoto").click(function () {
                if (xPosiotion == 0) {
                    xPosiotion = (-70 * 9) * lastThumbPhotoPage;
                } else if (xPosiotion != 0) {
                    xPosiotion += 70 * 9;
            }
                document.getElementById("thumbs").style.left = parseInt(xPosiotion) + "px";
        });
        }
    });
       </script>

       function HNR_LoadAlterHotels() {

		$("#divAlterHotels").ajaxError(function (e, xhr, settings, exception) {
		
			var errMsg = 'error in: ' + settings.url + ' \n' + 'error:\n' + xhr.responseText;        
			SendErrorLog("js function HNR_LoadAlterHotels error - ajax postback error : " + errMsg)
		});

		var now, duration;
		$.ajax({
		    type: 'POST',
		    url: "/pages/ajax/GetAlternativeHotels.aspx",
		    data:{ sfId: 3, langId: 1, hotId: 43042, currCode: "USD", cityId:"9590", queryString: "asq=VgfhI%2b8ejtenT5fmi1xjieylfdzVeXMLPGm11B5bQ09f6TVwMFbl2trvNxUHBG8dVFCPC09PwAuATtLmV0D1U1fdtOi7b2wr%2bSfzJbMiF%2fIA3bF7Vqe6ni2bpPSBM9e1IRlKei8wZYHadq7LBMFA0r0uJB3zgijBnHYwALQPbFUqhY05xkKf4%2bXMF6yjiQjSgZxwF0f6DnDDroq5NYt9TQ%3d%3d", langOpt:"True", countryId:3, abtest1618 : "False", abtest1730 : "False", abtest1937 : "True", abtest1937 : "True", abtest2267 : "False", abtest3193 : "True", abtest2861 : "True", abtest3588 : "True", isSendCorrectDeviceID : "True"}, 
	        beforeSend:function(){
	            now = new Date().getTime();
	        },
	        success:function (data) {
					    
	            var duration = new Date().getTime() - now;
	                Agoda.Stats.send(1, 3983, "43042", true, duration);
	            
						$("#divAlterHotels").unbind('ajaxError');                       
						        HNR_SetAlterHotels(data);
            }
	    });	 

		
	    Agoda.Stats.send(1, '3177', '0', false, 0);

	} //end function

	function HNR_SetAlterHotels(data) {
		
		if(data != ""){
			$("#divAlterHotels").empty().append(data);
			$(".alterhot").show();
		}else{
			$("#divAlterHotels").empty();
			$(".alterhot").hide();
		}
	}

      <script type="text/javascript">
       function setOpenUrl(linkObj, obj, id, endSentence) {

        var linkUrl = obj + "/pages/agoda/popup/popup_report_review.aspx?hotelReviewID=" + endSentence + "&amp;width=900&amp;height=500";

        $("a.modalpopupV1").attr("disabled", true);
        Agoda_initialPopupV1(linkObj, linkUrl);
        $("a.modalpopupV1").attr("disabled", false);
        $("a.modalpopupV1").attr("style", "display : block;");
        linkObj.href = "#id";
    }


    function Agoda_initialPopupV1(domClass, link) {
        var queryString = link;
        queryString = queryString.replace(/^[^\?]+\??/, '');
        var params = parseQueryPopup(queryString);

        if (typeof mp_closeTxt == 'undefined') {
            mp_closeTxt = domClass.getAttribute("closeText")
        }

        if (typeof mp_loadingText == 'undefined') {
            mp_loadingText = "Loading...";
        }

        var popupName = '';

        eval("option" + popupName + " = {"
            + "popupName: '" + popupName + "' || '',"
            + "titleText: domClass.getAttribute('popupTitle') || domClass.title || domClass.name || null,"
            + "contentUrl: '" + link + "' || domClass.alt || '#',"
            + "closeText: mp_closeTxt || domClass.getAttribute('closeText') || 'Close',"
            + "loadingImage: domClass.getAttribute('loadingImage') || '//cdn2.agoda.net/images/default/preload.gif',"
            + "loadingText: domClass.getAttribute('loadingText') || params['loadingtext'] || mp_loadingText,"
            + "popupWidth: domClass.getAttribute('popupWidth') || params['width'] || domClass.width || 630,"
            + "popupHeight: domClass.getAttribute('popupHeight') || params['height'] || domClass.height || 440,"
            + "popupSize: domClass.getAttribute('PopupSize') || params['PopupSize'] || '',"
            + "minWidth: 630,"
            + "minHeight: 440,"
            + "useScale: false,"
            + "popupScale: 80,"
            + "showLoadingPopup: domClass.getAttribute('showLoading') == 'false' ? false : true || true,"
            + "LoadingPosition: domClass.getAttribute('loadingPosition') || 'out',"
            + "popupFreeze: domClass.getAttribute('popupFreeze') == 'true' ? true : false || false,"
            + "noBorder: params['noborder'] == 1 ? true : false || false,"
            + "footerText: domClass.getAttribute('footerText') || '',"
            + "idModalPopup: 'MP_window" + popupName + "',"
            + "idIFrameContent: 'MP_iframeContent" + popupName + "',"
            + "idOverlay: 'MP_overlay" + popupName + "',"
            + "idLoad: 'MP_loading" + popupName + "',"
            + "idCloseButton: 'MP_closeButton" + popupName + "',"
            + "idHideSelect: 'MP_HideSelect" + popupName + "',"
            + "idParentFrame: domClass.getAttribute('parentName') || ''"
            + "}");

        eval("if (option" + popupName + ".popupSize.length &gt; 0) {"
                + "option" + popupName + ".useScale = true;"
                + "option" + popupName + ".popupScale = option" + popupName + ".popupSize;"
                + "option" + popupName + ".showLoadingPopup = true;"
                 + "option" + popupName + ".LoadingPosition = 'in';"
                + "option" + popupName + ".minWidth = 785;"
                + "option" + popupName + ".minHeight = 525;"
                + "} else {"
                + "option" + popupName + ".useScale = false;"
                + "}");

        //Show popup   
        eval("Agoda_showPopupV1('" + popupName + "');");
        eval("var useScale = option" + popupName + ".useScale;");

        if (useScale) {
            $(window).resize(function () {
                if (this.resizeTO) clearTimeout(this.resizeTO);
                this.resizeTO = setTimeout(function () {
                    $(this).trigger('resizeEnd');
                }, 200);
            });

            $(window).bind('resizeEnd', function () {
                if (document.getElementById(option.idIFrameContent)) {
                    eval("option" + popupName + ".contentUrl = '" + link + "'");
                }
                //Reload popup
                eval("Agoda_showPopupV1('" + popupName + "');");
            });
        }
    }

    function Agoda_showPopupV1(popupName) {
        eval("var _option = option" + popupName + ";");

        var popupWidth = _option.popupWidth;
        var popupHeight = _option.popupHeight;

        if (_option.useScale) {
            //Resizable popup
            popupWidth = ($(window).width() * _option.popupScale) / 100;
            popupHeight = ($(window).height() * _option.popupScale) / 100;

            if (popupWidth &lt; _option.minWidth) { popupWidth = _option.minWidth; }
            if (popupHeight &lt; _option.minHeight) { popupHeight = _option.minHeight; }

            if (popupWidth != _option.popupWidth || popupHeight != _option.popupHeight) {
                _option.popupWidth = popupWidth;
                _option.popupHeight = popupHeight;
            }
        }
        else {
            //Fixed size popup
            _option.popupWidth = popupWidth;
            _option.popupHeight = popupHeight;
        }

        //Save current width and height
        eval("option" + popupName + ".popupWidth = popupWidth;");
        eval("option" + popupName + ".popupHeight = popupHeight;");

        //Remove existing tag
        if ($("#" + _option.idOverlay).length &gt; 0) { $("#" + _option.idOverlay).remove(); }
        if ($("#" + _option.idLoad).length &gt; 0) { $("#" + _option.idLoad).remove(); }
        if ($("#" + _option.idModalPopup).length &gt; 0) { $("#" + _option.idModalPopup).remove(); }

        //Add popup tags
        var iframeWidth = popupWidth - 24;
        var iframeHeight = popupHeight - 30;

        $("body").append(Agoda_buildPopupContentV1(popupName, iframeWidth, iframeHeight));

        $("#" + _option.idOverlay).css({ opacity: 0.35 });

        $("#" + _option.idModalPopup).css({ marginLeft: '-' + parseInt((popupWidth / 2), 10) + 'px', width: popupWidth + 'px' });

        //fix exit popup before iframe loaded
        if (_option.idParentFrame != "") {
            var doc = document.getElementById(_option.idParentFrame).contentWindow.document;
            if (doc.attachEvent) {
                //for IE
                doc.attachEvent("onkeyup", function (e) {
                    var keycode = (e.keyChar) ? e.keyChar : ((e.keyCode) ? e.keyCode : e.which);
                    if (keycode == 27) { // close   
                        eval("Agoda_closePopupV1('" + popupName + "');");
                        return false;
                    }

                });
            }
            else {
                doc.addEventListener("keyup", function (e) {
                    var keycode = (e.keyChar) ? e.keyChar : ((e.keyCode) ? e.keyCode : e.which);
                    if (keycode == 27) { // close
                        eval("Agoda_closePopupV1('" + popupName + "');");
                        return false;
                    }
                }, false);
            }
        }

        if (!(jQuery.browser.msie &amp;&amp; jQuery.browser.version &lt; 7)) { // take away IE6
            $("#" + _option.idModalPopup).css({ marginTop: '-' + parseInt((popupHeight / 2), 10) + 'px' });
        }

        if (_option.showLoadingPopup == true &amp;&amp; _option.LoadingPosition == 'out') {
            $("#" + _option.idLoad).show();
            $("#" + _option.idModalPopup).css("display", "none");
        }
        else if (_option.showLoadingPopup == false) {
            $("#" + _option.idLoad).hide();
            $("#" + _option.idModalPopup).css("display", "block");
        } else {
            $("#" + _option.idLoad).show();
            $("#" + _option.idModalPopup).css("display", "block");
        }

        //Add popup events
        if (_option.popupFreeze == false) {
            $("#" + _option.idOverlay).click(function () {
                eval("Agoda_closePopupV1('" + popupName + "');");
                return false;
            });
            $("#" + _option.idCloseButton).click(function () {
                eval("Agoda_closePopupV1('" + popupName + "');");
                return false;
            });

            //Add keyboard event
            document.onkeyup = function (e) {
                if (e == null) { // ie
                    keycode = event.keyCode;
                } else { // mozilla
                    keycode = e.which;
                }
                if (keycode == 27) { // close
                    eval("Agoda_closePopupV1('" + popupName + "');");
                    return false;
                }
            };
        }

        $('iframe#' + _option.idIFrameContent).load(function () {
            if (_option.popupFreeze == false) {
                var doc = document.getElementById(_option.idIFrameContent).contentWindow.document;
                if (doc.attachEvent) {
                    //for IE
                    doc.attachEvent("onkeyup", function (e) {
                        var keycode = (e.keyChar) ? e.keyChar : ((e.keyCode) ? e.keyCode : e.which);
                        if (keycode == 27) { // close
                            eval("Agoda_closePopupV1('" + popupName + "');");
                            return false;
                        }
                    });
                }
                else {
                    doc.addEventListener("keyup", function (e) {
                        var keycode = (e.keyChar) ? e.keyChar : ((e.keyCode) ? e.keyCode : e.which);
                        if (keycode == 27) { // close
                            eval("Agoda_closePopupV1('" + popupName + "');");
                            return false;
                        }
                    }, false);
                }

                $("#" + _option.idLoad).hide();
            }

            $("#" + _option.idModalPopup).css("display", "block");
            $("#" + _option.idIFrameContent).css("display", "block");
            $('iframe#' + _option.idIFrameContent).focus();
        });
    }

    function Agoda_closePopupV1(popupName) {
        eval("var _option = option" + popupName + ";");

        $("#" + _option.idOverlay).unbind("click");
        $("#" + _option.idCloseButton).unbind("click");
        $("#" + _option.idModalPopup).fadeOut("fast", function () { $('#' + _option.idModalPopup + ',#' + _option.idOverlay + ",#" + _option.idHideSelect).trigger("unload").unbind().remove(); });

        $("#" + _option.idLoad).remove();

        if (this.resizeTO) this.resizeTO = null;
        $(window).unbind('resizeEnd');
        $(window).resize = "";

        document.onkeyup = "";

        if (_option.idParentFrame != '') {
            if (jQuery.browser.msie) {
                if ($('iframe#' + _option.idParentFrame) != null) {
                    if ($('iframe#' + _option.idParentFrame).get(0).contentWindow != null)
                        $('iframe#' + _option.idParentFrame).get(0).contentWindow.focus();
                }

            } else {
                $('iframe#' + _option.idParentFrame).focus();
            }
        }
    }

    function Agoda_buildPopupContentV1(popupName, iframeWidth, iframeHeight) {
        eval("var _option = option" + popupName + ";");

        //Add popup tags
        if (_option.useScale) {
            iframeHeight = iframeHeight - 80;
        }
        var content = "";

        if (typeof document.body.style.maxHeight === "undefined") {//if IE 6
            if (document.getElementById(_option.idHideSelect) === null) {//iframe to hide select elements in ie6
                content += "&lt;iframe id='" + _option.idHideSelect + "' class='mpopup_hideselect'&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;";
            }
        }

        content += "&lt;div id='" + _option.idOverlay + "' class='mpopup_overlay'&gt;&lt;/div&gt;";

        if (_option.showLoadingPopup == true) {
            if (_option.LoadingPosition == 'in') {
                content += "&lt;div id='" + _option.idModalPopup + "' class='mpopup_window'&gt;";
                content += "&lt;div id='" + _option.idLoad + "' class='mpopup_loading loading_nobd'&gt;&lt;img src='" + _option.loadingImage + "' /&gt;&lt;span&gt;" + _option.loadingText + "&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;";
            } else {
                content += "&lt;div id='" + _option.idLoad + "' class='mpopup_loading'&gt;&lt;img src='" + _option.loadingImage + "' /&gt;&lt;span&gt;" + _option.loadingText + "&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;";
                content += "&lt;div id='" + _option.idModalPopup + "' class='mpopup_window'&gt;";
            }
        }
        else {
            content += "&lt;div id='" + _option.idModalPopup + "' class='mpopup_window'&gt;";
            content += "&lt;div id='" + _option.idLoad + "' class='mpopup_loading loading_nobd'&gt;&lt;img src='" + _option.loadingImage + "' /&gt;&lt;span&gt;" + _option.loadingText + "&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;";
        }

        var removeBorderStr = "";
        if (_option.noBorder == true) {
            removeBorderStr = " border: 0; margin:0 12px 10px";
        }

        content += "&lt;div id='MP_header" + popupName + "' class='mpopup_header'&gt;";
        content += "&lt;table cellspacing='0' cellpadding='0' class='widthfull'&gt;";
        content += "&lt;tr&gt;";
        content += "&lt;td&gt;&lt;div id='MP_titleDiv" + popupName + "' class='mpopup_title'&gt;&lt;div id='MP_titleText" + popupName + "' class='fontmediumb'&gt;" + _option.titleText + "&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;";

        if (_option.popupFreeze == false) {
            content += "&lt;td&gt;&lt;div id='MP_closeDiv" + popupName + "' class='mpopup_btnclose'&gt;&lt;a href='#' id='" + _option.idCloseButton + "'&gt;" + _option.closeText + "&lt;span class='sprite_sec'&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;";
        }

        content += "&lt;/table&gt;";
        content += "&lt;/div&gt;";
        content += "&lt;div id='MP_divFrame" + popupName + "' class='mpopup_diviframe' style='" + removeBorderStr + "'&gt;&lt;iframe frameborder='0' hspace='0' class='iframeClass' src='" + _option.contentUrl + "' id='" + _option.idIFrameContent + "' name='" + _option.idIFrameContent + "' style='width:" + iframeWidth + "px;height:" + iframeHeight + "px;' scrolling='no'&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;";

        if (_option.footerText != "") {
            content += "&lt;div id='MP_footer" + popupName + "' class='mpopup_footer'&gt;";
            content += "&lt;table cellspacing='0' cellpadding='0' class='widthfull'&gt;";
            content += "&lt;tr&gt;";
            content += "&lt;td&gt;&lt;div id='MP_FooterDiv" + popupName + "'&gt;&lt;div id='MP_footerText" + popupName + "' class='fontsmallb tex_left'&gt;" + _option.footerText + "&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;";
            content += "&lt;/table&gt;";
            content += "&lt;/div&gt;";
        }

        content += "&lt;/div&gt;";

        return content;
    }

    function parseQueryPopup(query) {
        var Params = {};
        if (!query) { return Params; } // return empty object
        var Pairs = query.split(/[;&amp;]/);
        for (var i = 0; i &lt; Pairs.length; i++) {
            var KeyVal = Pairs[i].split('=');
            if (!KeyVal || KeyVal.length != 2) { continue; }
            var key = unescape(KeyVal[0]);
            var val = unescape(KeyVal[1]);
            val = val.replace(/\+/g, ' ');
            Params[key] = val;
        }
        return Params;
    }

		$("#ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_ContentMain_LookBooked_1_pnlLookedBooked").attr("alreadyLoaded", "true");


		$(".divRateContent").empty().append("&lt;img style='width:47px;height:47px !important;margin:5px 0px;' src='//cdn0.agoda.net/images/default/preload.gif'&gt;");

		//Set error event handler
		$("#ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_ContentMain_LookBooked_1_pnlLookedBooked").ajaxError(function (e, xhr, settings, exception) {
			//alert('error in: ' + settings.url + ' \n' + 'error:\n' + xhr.responseText);
			//$("#ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_ContentMain_LookBooked_1_pnlLookedBooked").empty().append('error in: ' + settings.url + ' \n' + 'error:\n' + xhr.responseText);
			var errMsg = 'error in: ' + settings.url + ' \n' + 'error:\n' + xhr.responseText;
			//alert('error in: ' + settings.url + ' \n' + 'error:\n' + xhr.responseText);
			SendErrorLog("js function LoadContent error - ajax postback error : " + errMsg)
		});
	    var now, duration;
	    $.ajax({
	        type: 'POST',
	        url: "/pages/ajax/GetHotels.aspx",
	        data:{ func: "LookBookedHotelRate", HotelIds: "197727,65794,51481,276198", cityId: "9590", queryString: "asq=VgfhI%2b8ejtenT5fmi1xjieylfdzVeXMLPGm11B5bQ09f6TVwMFbl2trvNxUHBG8dVFCPC09PwAuATtLmV0D1U1fdtOi7b2wr%2bSfzJbMiF%2fIA3bF7Vqe6ni2bpPSBM9e1IRlKei8wZYHadq7LBMFA0r0uJB3zgijBnHYwALQPbFUqhY05xkKf4%2bXMF6yjiQjSgZxwF0f6DnDDroq5NYt9TQ%3d%3d" ,langOpt:"True",countryId:3, abtest1618 : "False", abtest1937 : "True", calledFrom : 1, abtest1937 : "True", abtest2267 : "False", abtest3193 : "True", abtest2861: "True", abtest3588: "True", isSendCorrectDeviceID: "True"},
	        beforeSend:function(){
	            now = new Date().getTime();
	        },
	        success:function (data) {
	            
	            duration = new Date().getTime() - now;

	                Agoda.Stats.send(1, 3983, "197727,65794,51481,276198", true, duration);

						$("#ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_ContentMain_LookBooked_1_pnlLookedBooked").unbind('ajaxError');
						SetLookBookedRate(data);
	        },
	    });	   
	    Agoda.Stats.send(1, '3184', '0', false, 0);

	} //end function

	function SetLookBookedRate(data) {
		var hotelList = eval(data);
		var hotel;
		var soldOutText = "&lt;p class='fontsmallb red' style='margin-top:15px'&gt;Sold out&lt;/p&gt;";  //22326=Sold out

	    if ('True' == 'True' )
	    {
	        var hasZeroPrice = CheckHasZeroPrice(hotelList);
	        if(hasZeroPrice)
	        {
	            $('div.divRateContent').each(function (index) {
	                hotel = FindHotel($(this).attr("hotelId"), hotelList);
	                if (hotel != null) {
	                    if (hotel.Promotion != null &amp;&amp; hotel.Promotion != "") {
	                        $("div.promotionContent[hotelId='" + hotel.HotelId + "']").empty().append(hotel.Promotion);
	                    }
	                }
	            });

	            $('div.divHotelContent').each(function (index) {      
	                $content= $("div.content").eq(index).clone();
	                $("div.panelContent").eq(index).empty();
	                $(this).empty().append($content);
	                $(this).find('.lblCustName , .sprite_f, .lblReviewDate').wrapAll('&lt;div class="reviewInfo"&gt;');
	            });

	            $('div.divRateContent').empty().append("");
	            $('.tdHotelImg').width('30%');
	        }
	        else{

		$("div.divRateContent").each(function (index) {
	                hotel = FindHotel($(this).attr("hotelId"), hotelList);
	                if (hotel == null) {
	                    $(this).empty().append("");
	                } else {
	                    $(this).empty().append(hotel.PriceContent);
	                    //Set Promotion                       

	                    if (hotel.Promotion != null &amp;&amp; hotel.Promotion != "") {

	                        $("div.promotionContent[hotelId='" + hotel.HotelId + "']").empty().append(hotel.Promotion);
	                    }

	                }


	            });
	        }
	    }
	    else{

	        $("div.divRateContent").each(function (index) {
			hotel = FindHotel($(this).attr("hotelId"), hotelList);
			if (hotel == null) {
				$(this).empty().append("");
			} else {
				$(this).empty().append(hotel.PriceContent);
				//Set Promotion                       

				if (hotel.Promotion != null &amp;&amp; hotel.Promotion != "") {

					$("div.promotionContent[hotelId='" + hotel.HotelId + "']").empty().append(hotel.Promotion);
				}

			}


		});
	    }

	}

    function CheckHasZeroPrice(hotelList)
    {
        if(hotelList != undefined &amp;&amp; hotelList != null){
            for (i = 0; i &lt; hotelList.length; i++) {
               
                var priceContent = hotelList[i].PriceContent!= null ? hotelList[i].PriceContent.split('&lt;/span&gt;')[1].trim() : "0.00";
                if (priceContent == '0.00') {
                    return true;
                }
            }
        }else return true;

        //return true;
    }

	function FindHotel(hotelId, hotelList) {
		for (i = 0; i &lt; hotelList.length; i++) {

			if (hotelId == hotelList[i].HotelId) {
				return hotelList[i];
			}
		}

		//can not find
		return null;

	}


	$(document).ready(function () {

		$(window).scroll(function () {
			//check if reach the area to load.
			if ($(window).scrollTop() + $(window).height() &gt;= $("#ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_ContentMain_LookBooked_1_pnlLookedBooked").offset().top) {
				if ($("#ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_ContentMain_LookBooked_1_pnlLookedBooked").attr("alreadyLoaded") != "true") {
					LoadContent();

				}
			}

		});

	});
     </script>

     <script language="javascript" type="text/javascript">
      $(document).ready(function () {
                function JumpToHashLocation(clickedElement) {
                    $(document).on("click", clickedElement, function () {

                        var currentAttrHref = $(this).attr('href');
                        var $target = $(currentAttrHref).next("div.heading");


                        if ($target.find("strong").hasClass("plus")) {
                            $target.next(".desContent").slideToggle(500);
                            $target.find("strong").removeClass("plus");
                            $target.find("strong.sprite").addClass("minus");
                        }
                        location.hash = currentAttrHref;
                    });
                }

                JumpToHashLocation("a.policies");
                JumpToHashLocation("a.usefulinformation");
                JumpToHashLocation("a.important_information");

                if (location.hash == "#HotelPolicies") {
                    // alert("hotel policies hash");
                    $("a.policies").trigger("click");
                } else if (location.hash == "#UsefulInformation") {
                    //alert("useful information hash");
                    $("a.usefulinformation").trigger("click");
                }
                else if (location.hash == "#ImportantNotice") {
                    // alert("important notice hash");
                    $("a.important_information").trigger("click");
                }
            });
     </script>

                        document.getElementById("loading").style.display = "";
                        document.getElementById("ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_AlternateHotelLis_RecentlyHotels1_lbClearHistory").disabled = true;
                    }
                }
            }
        } catch (Error) {
            SendErrorLog("js function startRequest on RecentlyHotel error : " + Error.message);
        }
    }
    function endRequest(sender, e) {
        try {
            //disable search button during the AJAX call
            if (postBackElement != null) {

     <script type="text/javascript">
      function generateSearchActionMIN361(isoccfreesearch, landingMethod, inputText, isLeftSearchBox) {
                var params = "dp_objectType=" + 7;
                params += "&amp;dp_objectId=43042";
                params += "&amp;dp_cityId=9590";
                params += "&amp;dp_countryId=3";
                params += "&amp;dp_iofs=" + isoccfreesearch;
                params += "&amp;dp_lm=" + landingMethod;

                if (landingMethod === 2) {
                    params += "&amp;dp_searchText=" + encodeURIComponent(inputText);
                }
                else {
                    params += "&amp;dp_hotelId=43042";
                }

                if(isLeftSearchBox) {
                    params += "&amp;dp_checkIn=" + $("input[id*='_hotelleftsearchbox_arrivaldate']").val();
                    params += "&amp;dp_checkOut=" + $("input[id*='_hotelleftsearchbox_departdate']").val();
                    params += "&amp;dp_nights=" + $("select[id*='_hotelleftsearchbox_ddlNights_left']").val();
                    
                    var occoption = $("select[id*='_hotelleftsearchbox_ddlGuests']").val();
                    if (occoption == 1) {
                        params += "&amp;dp_rooms=1&amp;dp_adults=2&amp;dp_children=0";
                    }
                    else if (occoption == 3) {
                        params += "&amp;dp_rooms=1&amp;dp_adults=1&amp;dp_children=0";
                    }
                    else {
                        params += "&amp;dp_rooms=" + $("select[id*='_hotelleftsearchbox_ddlRoom']").val();
                        params += "&amp;dp_adults=" + $("select[id*='_hotelleftsearchbox_ddlAdult']").val();
                        params += "&amp;dp_children=" + $("select[id*='_hotelleftsearchbox_ddlChildren']").val(); 
                    }
                }
                else {
                    params += "&amp;dp_checkIn=" + $("input[id*='_hotelSearchbox1_arrivaldate']").val();
                    params += "&amp;dp_checkOut=" + $("input[id*='_hotelSearchbox1_departdate']").val();
                    params += "&amp;dp_nights=" + $("select[id*='_hotelSearchbox1_ddlNights']").val();
                    params += "&amp;dp_rooms=1";
                    params += "&amp;dp_adults=2";
                    params += "&amp;dp_children=0";
                }
                
                var searchAction = "/Search/ajax/17142418/7/3/1/1/9590/1/";
                if(searchAction.indexOf("?") &gt; -1) {
                    searchAction += "&amp;" + params
                }
                else {
                    searchAction += "?" + params
                }
                return searchAction;
            }

            function doSearchMIN361(obj) {
                if (obj) {
                    var isValidSearch = false;
                    var isLeftSearchBox = obj.id.indexOf("hotelleftsearchbox") &gt; -1;
                    var landingMethod = 4;
                    var isoccfreesearch = false;
                    var inputText = "";                    
                    var parentControlID = obj.id.replace("_SearchButton", "");
                    ControlID = parentControlID + "_";

                    if(isLeftSearchBox) {
                        //Check if user search with this hotel name
                        var objInputId = "";
                        var objInput = $("#" + parentControlID + "_TextSearch1_txtSearch");
                        if (objInput &amp;&amp; objInput.length &gt; 0) {
                            landingMethod = 2;
                            objInputId = objInput[0].id;
                            inputText = $(objInput[0]).val();
                            var hotelName = $(".header_hotel span[id*='_lblHotelName']").text();
                            if(hotelName.substring(0, 50) === inputText.substring(0, 50)) {
                                landingMethod = 4;
                            }                    
                            RemoveSpecialCharacter(objInputId);
                            if(isoccfreesearch) {
                                isValidSearch = doTextSearch(objInput[0].id);
                            }
                            else {
                                isValidSearch = validateSearchCriteria_2317(parentControlID) &amp;&amp; doTextSearch(objInput[0].id);
                            }
                        }
                        else {
                            isValidSearch = doSearch();
                        }
                    }
                    else {
                        isValidSearch = doSearch();
                    }
                    
                    if (isValidSearch) {                        
                        $.ajax({
                            type: "POST",
                            url: generateSearchActionMIN361(isoccfreesearch, landingMethod, inputText, isLeftSearchBox),
                            data: "{ method: " + landingMethod + "}",
                            contentType: "application/json; charset=utf-8",
                            dataType: "json",
                            success: function (data) {                                
                                window.location = data;
                            },
                            error: function (ex) {
                                return true; //return true to post back to sever. I should be the same behavior as the a version.
                            }
                        });
                    }
                    return false
                }
            }
     </script>

  <script type="text/javascript">
   var asq = 'asq=VgfhI%2b8ejtenT5fmi1xjieylfdzVeXMLPGm11B5bQ09f6TVwMFbl2trvNxUHBG8dVFCPC09PwAuATtLmV0D1U1fdtOi7b2wr%2bSfzJbMiF%2fIA3bF7Vqe6ni2bpPSBM9e1IRlKei8wZYHadq7LBMFA0r0uJB3zgijBnHYwALQPbFUqhY05xkKf4%2bXMF6yjiQjSgZxwF0f6DnDDroq5NYt9TQ%3d%3d';
	var ldomain = '';

	// ** Suppress Ajax Library Javascript Errors *     
	Sys.Application.add_load(AppLoad_Main);
	function AppLoad_Main() {
		Sys.WebForms.PageRequestManager.getInstance().add_endRequest(endRequest_Main);
	}

	function endRequest_Main(sender, e) {
		bindQueryStringOnLinks();
	}

	function isAgodaURL(url) {
		var agodaURLs = ["agoda.", "localhost"];
		var pattImg = /\.(gif|jpg|png)\b/i;

		if (url != null &amp;&amp; url.charAt(0) != "#" &amp;&amp; url.indexOf("javascript:") == -1 &amp;&amp; url.indexOf("mailto:") == -1 &amp;&amp; url.indexOf("javascript:") == -1 &amp;&amp; url.match(pattImg) == null) {
			if (url.charAt(0) == "/") {
				return true;
			}

			for (var i = 0; i &lt; agodaURLs.length; i++) {
				if (url.indexOf(agodaURLs[i]) != -1) { //is agoda url
					return true;
				}
			}
		}

		//does not match anything.
		return false;
	}

	function bindQueryStringOnLinks() {

		$("a[href]").not(".notabsafe").each(function () {

			if (isAgodaURL($(this).attr('href'))) {

				var originalLink = $(this).attr('href');
				var innerElement = $(this).html();
				$(this).attr('href', getLink(originalLink));
				$(this).html(innerElement);
			}

		});

		$("input[alt^='/']").each(function () {

			if (isAgodaURL($(this).attr('alt'))) {

				var originalLink = $(this).attr('alt');
				var innerElement = $(this).html();
				$(this).attr('alt', getLink(originalLink));
				$(this).html(innerElement);
			}

		});

	}

	function getLink(url) {
		var originalLink = url
		var newLink;
		if (originalLink.indexOf("asq") == -1) {
			newLink = getCombinedQuery(originalLink, asq);
		} else {
			newLink = originalLink
		}
		newLink = getDomainLink(newLink);

		return newLink;
	}

	function getCombinedQuery(originalLink, agodaQuery) {

		var arrOriginalLink;
		if (originalLink.indexOf("#") != -1) {
			//it contains '#' in link
			arrOriginalLink = originalLink.split("#");
			originalLink = arrOriginalLink[0];
		}

		var result = "";
		if (originalLink.indexOf("?") == -1) {
			result = originalLink + "?" + agodaQuery
			if (arrOriginalLink != null &amp;&amp; arrOriginalLink.length &gt; 1) { //it contains '#' in link bind it back.
				result = result + "#" + arrOriginalLink[1];
			}
			return result;
		}



		var originalQuery = originalLink.split("?")[1];
		var arrOriginalQuery = originalQuery.split("&amp;");
		var newAgodaQuery = "";
		var arrAgodaQuery = agodaQuery.split("&amp;");
		var arrRemovedIndex = new Array();
		for (var i in arrOriginalQuery) {
			var qname = arrOriginalQuery[i].toString().split("=")[0].toLowerCase();
			//qname.replace(/^\s+|\s+$/g,"") =  Trim()                   
			if (qname != null &amp;&amp; qname.replace(/^\s+|\s+$/g, "") != "" &amp;&amp; agodaQuery.toLowerCase().indexOf(qname) != -1) {
				//remember index of AgodaQuery to be removed                        
				for (var j in arrAgodaQuery) {

					if (arrAgodaQuery[j].toLowerCase().indexOf(qname) != -1) {
						arrRemovedIndex.push(j);
					}
				}

			}
		}

		//remove query name from Agoda Query as it duplicate.
		var isFirst = true;
		for (var i in arrAgodaQuery) {

			var isRemoved = false;
			for (var j in arrRemovedIndex) {
				if (i == arrRemovedIndex[j]) {
					isRemoved = true;
				}
			}

			if (!isRemoved) {
				if (isFirst) {
					newAgodaQuery = arrAgodaQuery[i];
					isFirst = false;

				} else {
					newAgodaQuery = newAgodaQuery + "&amp;" + arrAgodaQuery[i];
				}
			}

		}


		if (originalLink.charAt(originalLink.length - 1) == "&amp;") { //last char of originalLink is "&amp;"
			result = originalLink + newAgodaQuery;
		}
		else {
			result = originalLink + "&amp;" + newAgodaQuery;
		}

		if (arrOriginalLink != null &amp;&amp; arrOriginalLink.length &gt; 1) { //it contains '#' in link bind it back.
			result = result + "#" + arrOriginalLink[1];
		}

		return result;
	}

	function getDomainLink(url) {
		if (ldomain == null || ldomain == "" || url == null || url == "") {
			return url;
		}

		var arrUrl = url.split("?");
		var urlDomain = arrUrl[0];

		if (urlDomain.indexOf(ldomain) != -1) {
			return url;
		}

		if (url.substring(0, 2) == "//") {
			return url;
		}

		if (urlDomain.charAt(0) == "/") {
			return ldomain + url;
		}

		if (urlDomain.indexOf(".agoda.") != -1) {

			var arrUrlDomain = urlDomain.split("/");
			var finalUrl = "";
			var isFirst = true;
			for (var i in arrUrlDomain) {
				var agodaTextIndex = arrUrlDomain[i].indexOf(".agoda.");
				if (agodaTextIndex != -1) {
					arrUrlDomain[i] = arrUrlDomain[i].substring(0, agodaTextIndex) + ".agoda.com" + ldomain;
				}

				if (arrUrlDomain[i] != null &amp;&amp; arrUrlDomain[i] != "") {
					if (isFirst) {
						finalUrl = arrUrlDomain[i];
						if (arrUrlDomain[i].indexOf("http") != -1) {
							finalUrl = arrUrlDomain[i] + "//";
						}
						isFirst = false;
					} else {
						if (finalUrl.charAt(finalUrl.length - 1) == "/") {
							finalUrl = finalUrl + arrUrlDomain[i];
						} else {
							finalUrl = finalUrl + "/" + arrUrlDomain[i];
						}

					}
				}

			}

			if (arrUrl.length == 2) {
				finalUrl = finalUrl + "?" + arrUrl[1];
			}

			return finalUrl;

		}

		return url;
	}

	$(document).ready(function () {

		bindQueryStringOnLinks();

	});
  </script>

  <script type="text/javascript">
   $(document).ready(function () {           
                var _this = $(this);

                var cidInAddress = _getTrackingParameter("cid|siteid|site_id", window.location.href);
                var tagInAddress = _getTrackingParameter("tag", window.location.href);

                var allAnchors = $('a');

                if (cidInAddress != null || tagInAddress != null) {
                    allAnchors.each(function (idx) {
                        // Loop each element's link
                        var originalHref = $(this).attr('href');
                        $(this).attr('href', _addTrackingParameters(originalHref, cidInAddress, tagInAddress));
                    });
                }

                function _addTrackingParameters(originalHref, cid, tag) {
                    if (originalHref != undefined) {
                        //Check for javascript and div id in href
                        if (_isFunctionOrStartWithHash(originalHref) == false) {
                            var patchedHref = originalHref;
                            var hashParameter = "";
                            var hasHash = /(#)/.exec(originalHref);
                            if (hasHash != null) {
                                var result = originalHref.split("#");
                                hashParameter = "#" + result[1];
                                patchedHref = result[0];
                            }

                            // Check not to patch cid if it's -1 for SEO 
                            if (cid !== "-1") {
                                patchedHref = _addParameter(patchedHref, "cid", cid);
                            }
                            
                            patchedHref = _addParameter(patchedHref, "tag", tag);
                            patchedHref += hashParameter;

                            return patchedHref;
                        }
                    }
                    return originalHref;
                }

                function _isFunctionOrStartWithHash(href) {
                    var startWithHash = /(^#)/.exec(href);
                    var hasFunction = /(^javascript)/.exec(href);

                    if (startWithHash == null &amp;&amp; hasFunction == null) {
                        return false;
                    } else {
                        return true;
                    }
                }

                function _addParameter(url, name, value) {
                    if (value != null &amp;&amp; _getTrackingParameter(name, url) == null) {
                        url += ((url.indexOf('?') &gt;= 0) ? '&amp;' : '?') + name + "=" + value;
                    }
                    return url;
                }

                function _getTrackingParameter(name, uri) {
                    var matchRegEx = new RegExp('[?|&amp;](' + name + ')=' + '([^&amp;;]+?)(&amp;|#|;|$)', 'i').exec(uri) || [, ""];
                    if (matchRegEx[2] == undefined) {
                        return null;
                    }
                    return decodeURIComponent(matchRegEx[2].replace(/\+/g, '%20')) || null;
                }

                function _getUrlVars() {
                    var vars = [], hash;
                    var hashes = window.location.href.slice(window.location.href.indexOf('?') + 1).split('&amp;');
                    for (var i = 0; i &lt; hashes.length; i++) {
                        hash = hashes[i].split('=');
                        vars.push(hash[0]);
                        vars[hash[0]] = hash[1];
                    }
                    return vars;
                }
            });
  </script>
